---
layout: default
title: Interns (ongoing)
category: jobs
---

<p>OCCRP hires interns to do daily news stories, documentary production, support social media effort, for research and for other general tasks.  Interns are given in-house training and attend biweekly training classes. Terms are 3 months to 6 months with extensions possible up to one year.  Shorter time periods are not available.  International interns are not paid.  Regional or local interns with citizenship from the region working in our offices in Tbilisi, Bucharest and Sarajevo are paid a small honorarium.  Availability is limited.  Those interested should send an email with links to stories or a letter of interest to drew (at) occrp.org.</p>
